== Overview ==
<b>eGanglia</b> lets users connect with the Ganglia Monitoring System using gmetric
== Usage ==
Use {@link gmetric}<code>:announce/X</code> functions to interact directly with gmetric.<br />
Implement {@link gen_metric} behavior to define new custom metrics. Use {@link metric_group} to announce them.
